data.description: This spacious 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is located in the River Club subdivision and offers amenities such as a Swim/Tennis/Play area. As you enter the home, you are greeted by a welcoming foyer. The main level includes a formal living room, formal dining room, an eat-in kitchen with a breakfast bar and pantry, and a large family room with a fireplace. There is also a half bath on this level. The upper level features 2 additional bathrooms and oversized secondary bedrooms. The primary bedroom is a private en-suite with a soaking tub, double vanities, and dual closets. The 4th bedroom is spacious enough to be divided into 2 rooms. The home also includes a two-car garage, driveway, backyard patio, and an exterior storage shed.  Sold As-Is. Preferred closing attorney Chalker & Chalker.
